WEBVTT

00:00:07.455 --> 00:00:11.936
In 1898, Marie and Pierre Curie 
discovered radium.

00:00:11.936 --> 00:00:14.005
Claimed to have restorative properties,

00:00:14.005 --> 00:00:15.786
radium was added to toothpaste,

00:00:15.786 --> 00:00:16.657
medicine,

00:00:16.657 --> 00:00:17.418
water,

00:00:17.418 --> 00:00:18.615
and food.

00:00:18.615 --> 00:00:20.486
A glowing, luminous green,

00:00:20.486 --> 00:00:24.007
it was also used in beauty products
and jewelry.

00:00:24.007 --> 00:00:26.297
It wasn't until the mid-20th century

00:00:26.297 --> 00:00:30.265
we realized that radium's harmful
effects as a radioactive element